Quiqr is an open source project and we strive to form a healty, open and inspiring community. To everyone who likes to give a positive contribution&hellip; feel welcome!
We are organized on GitHub and currently our main projects are&hellip;
Quiqr Desktop - The Quiqr Desktop Application project. Quiqr Community Templates - Community driven list of Quiqr Site templates. The Quiqr Book - The Quiqr documentation project for both users and developers.

Quiqr is available for Mac, Windows and Linux. Here are the latest installers.
Quiqr for macOS reading&hellip;
Open the disk image and copy the Quiqr app to your Applications folder.
Quiqr for Windows reading&hellip;
After download execute the .exe-file to install Quiqr.
Quiqr for Linux reading&hellip;
Older versions All earlier versions and binaries for other platforms are located on GitHub
